OL,3,C'Surge' in Alabama rot: How to spot
OL,4,Cthe deadly dog disease
OL,6,FThe disease damages dogs' blood
OL,7,Fvessels, cutting off blood supply to
OL,8,Fareas of the skin and sometimes the
OL,9,Finternal organs, which causes skin
OL,10,Fsores and can lead to kidney failure
OL,12,FBritish dog owners and walkers have
OL,13,Fbeen warned of a "flesh-eating"
OL,14,Fdisease affecting pets, with new cases
OL,15,Fconfirmed across the UK.
OL,17,FA number of cases have been reported
OL,18,Fthis year in Wales, Scotland and the
OL,19,FNorth of England.
