OL,3,C'Surge' in Alabama rot: How to spot
OL,4,Cthe deadly dog disease
OL,6,FIt's particularly prevalent at this
OL,7,Ftime of year when the ground is soggy
OL,8,Fdue to increased rainfall.
OL,10,FHere's what to watch out for, to stop
OL,11,Fthe deadly disorder developing on your
OL,12,Ffour-legged friend.
OL,14,FWhat is Alabama rot?
OL,16,FAlabama rot, otherwise known as
OL,17,FCutaneous and Renal Glomerular
OL,18,FVasculopathy (CRGV), is a disease that
OL,19,Faffects dogs.
