OL,3,C'Surge' in Alabama rot: How to spot
OL,4,Cthe deadly dog disease
OL,6,FIt damages the blood vessels in the
OL,7,Fskin and kidneys, which causes visible
OL,8,Fsores on the skin and can lead to
OL,9,Fsevere organ dysfunction and
OL,10,Fultimately kidney failure.
OL,12,FThe cause of the disease is currently
OL,13,Funknown, though research is ongoing.
OL,15,FAlabama rot was first identified in
OL,16,Fgreyhounds in the United States in the
OL,17,F1980s but there have been reports of
OL,18,Fthe disease across the UK.
