OL,3,C'Surge' in Alabama rot: How to spot
OL,4,Cthe deadly dog disease
OL,6,FIn 2012, just six cases were reported
OL,7,Fin the UK, but this number has
OL,8,Fcontinued to rise each year since.
OL,10,FMost reports come from pet owners who
OL,11,Fwalk their dogs in the countryside,
OL,12,Fand most cases are reported during
OL,13,Fwinter and spring.
OL,15,FGenerally, cases are rare in the
OL,16,Fsummer months compared to the colder
OL,17,Fmonths.
